    "data_completeness": {
      "description": "Data completeness score = (number of user-provided optional features) / (total optional features). Calculated in the mobile app. A score of 1.0 means all optional fields were filled by the user; 0.0 means all used defaults. This score does NOT affect model confidence \u2014 it is purely informational for the user and for analytics.",
